meta {
  name: Activate factor (passcode)
  type: http
  seq: 2
}

post {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/authn/factors/{{factorId}}/lifecycle/activate
  body: json
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Content-Type: application/json
}

body:json {
  {
    "stateToken": "{{stateToken}}",
    "passCode": ""
  }
}

docs {
Activates a pending factor by submitting the passcode the user received (SMS, voice, email, TOTP). The factor moves to ACTIVE.

For Push factors, the activation lifecycle is different — use the activation polling URL embedded in the response from `Enroll factor`.
}
